nodes.text: R4-F5 was an R4-P astromech droid that was permanently integrated into the Delta-7 Aethersprite-class light interceptor of Jedi Master Plo Koon. At the end of the Clone Wars, the droid was killed along with its master on the planet Cato Neimoidia when their ship was destroyed by Clone Captain CT-55/11-9009 during the execution of Order 66. R4-F5 had a blue-green dome with grey paneling.
